decks.notes: This deck focuses on quickly building up +1/+1 counters on creatures using Hardened Scales and Agatha's Soul Cauldron, while also utilizing support cards like Zabaz, the Glimmerwasp and The Ozolith to maximize the value of those counters. With a mix of modular creatures like Arcbound Ravager and Walking Ballista, along with powerful artifacts and land synergies, this aggro deck aims to overwhelm opponents with a swarm of buffed creatures and versatile threats. The inclusion of control elements like Pithing Needle and Soul-Guide Lantern helps to disrupt opponent strategies and maintain board dominance.
